properties.name: Shooty Duck 2: Lost Feathers
properties.description: You're a Duck. And you've been living in your pond's dungeons for a looooong time, then one day, the Slimean army invades Pondungeondia (Your Pond's Dungeon) and they stole the feathers of your dead brother who was killed during the Slimo-Ducki war of 1994. Now you'll have to get em' back!
properties.author: LSID Studios
